### D. Output Order

After the analysis block is approved (or if generating without approval is requested), produce artifacts in this exact order:

```
1. Models          → feature-name.model.ts
2. Service         → feature-name.service.ts
3. Child components (leaf nodes first — deepest in tree)
   3a. [ChildComponent].component.ts
   3b. [ChildComponent].component.html
   3c. [ChildComponent].component.scss
4. Page component (last — depends on all children)
   4a. feature-name.component.ts
   4b. feature-name.component.html
   4c. feature-name.component.scss
5. Route definition (if new feature)
   5a. feature-name.routes.ts
6. Responsive notes
7. Accessibility notes
```

Never generate the page component before its child components. Never generate TypeScript before the model interfaces it depends on.

