### G. Decision Trees

#### "What layout component do I need?"
```
Is this a full-page layout with sidebar?
  YES → ejs-sidebar (right, Push type) + ejs-appbar + content area
  NO → Is this a split content area (list + detail)?
    YES → ejs-splitter (RTL: list panel right, detail panel left)
    NO → Is this a dashboard with resizable panels?
      YES → ejs-dashboardlayout
      NO → Standard CSS grid with layout tokens
```

#### "What input component do I need?"
```
Is it a date or time value?
  YES → ejs-datepicker / ejs-daterangepicker / ejs-datetimepicker / ejs-timepicker
  NO → Is it a selection from a list?
    YES → ≤5 options? → ejs-radiobutton
          Long list + search? → ejs-combobox
          Long list no search? → ejs-dropdownlist
          Multi-select? → ejs-multiselect
          Hierarchical? → ejs-dropdowntree
    NO → Is it a number?
      YES → ejs-numerictextbox
      NO → Is it a formatted value (phone, ID)?
        YES → ejs-maskedtextbox
        NO → Is it long text?
          YES → ejs-textbox [multiline]="true"
          NO → ejs-textbox
```

#### "What feedback component do I need?"
```
Is it after a completed action (save, delete, create)?
  YES → ejs-toast (auto-dismisses in 5s)
  NO → Is it a persistent inline message within the page?
    YES → ejs-message
    NO → Is it a loading state for a content area?
      YES → ejs-skeleton
      NO → Is it a loading state for a button/inline action?
        YES → ejs-spinner inside ejs-button
        NO → Is it a long-running operation with progress?
          YES → ejs-progressbar
          NO → Is it a count or status indicator on a nav item?
            YES → ejs-badge
```

#### "Does this need a dialog or a new page?"
```
Is the form ≤ 10 fields?
  YES → ejs-dialog with form inside
  NO → Is it a multi-step flow?
    YES → New page with ejs-stepper
    NO → New page (full-page form)
```

#### "Is this a new component or a shared one?"
```
Is this UI pattern used in 2+ places in the product?
  YES → shared/components/
  NO → Is it a UI pattern used across 2+ Khwarizmi products?
    YES → shared/components/ (design system candidate)
    NO → features/[feature]/components/
```

